column3: Just received them today.  They are so precious!

I like books. Other than that, let me share my latest approach to earring guards with you--if you are using the little plastic ones, use three or four at once, because I have had one slip off and make me lose an earring. If you are looking at hook earrings, the ones with a bend in them are probably at less risk of falling out. The straight ones absolutely demand guards, and, as I say, if you are going to stick to cheap plastic ones, probably three or four at once.
I am so excited to get these earrings but I’m sad it’s cracked . I definitely world purchase again
